    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在得知自己妆没化好就跑来学校后，贯彻完美主义的时尚辣妹森本星大受打击。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1864720/extras/d5176f319eedb77cf884d20ae8a25498.poster.avif?t=1750976836\" width=600 height=80 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1864720/extras/d5176f319eedb77cf884d20ae8a25498.webm?t=1750976836\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1864720/extras/d5176f319eedb77cf884d20ae8a25498.mp4?t=1750976836\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1864720/extras/06f3ff8f0ee68559df78398d17fed44b.poster.avif?t=1750976836\" width=600 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1864720/extras/06f3ff8f0ee68559df78398d17fed44b.webm?t=1750976836\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1864720/extras/06f3ff8f0ee68559df78398d17fed44b.mp4?t=1750976836\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >她发现自己居住的边远小镇突发异象、变得如同恶梦一般。街道似乎被弃置许久，通往异度建筑的传送门若隐若现，学生们受某种诡异的“屏息游戏”影响而变得疯狂，远处森林里更有一道谜之光束注视着她的一举一动。森本星试图逃离这个扭曲的新世界，但是小镇边缘发出的金光一直在阻挠她…… </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1864720/extras/cc44be751143eac193ada48acb7612fb.poster.avif?t=1750976836\" width=600 height=80 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1864720/extras/cc44be751143eac193ada48acb7612fb.webm?t=1750976836\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1864720/extras/cc44be751143eac193ada48acb7612fb.mp4?t=1750976836\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1864720/extras/fee49b97a46b1dd9f76e086442c2f8a3.poster.avif?t=1750976836\" width=600 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1864720/extras/fee49b97a46b1dd9f76e086442c2f8a3.webm?t=1750976836\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1864720/extras/fee49b97a46b1dd9f76e086442c2f8a3.mp4?t=1750976836\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 监视器视角搭配怀旧艺术风格。 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 永不过时的解谜游戏玩法。 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 探索废弃高中以及其他异界场所。 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 完全配音的角色对话和过场动画。 </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1864720/extras/69094bec872134a08d500dd306940c56.poster.avif?t=1750976836\" width=600 height=80 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1864720/extras/69094bec872134a08d500dd306940c56.webm?t=1750976836\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1864720/extras/69094bec872134a08d500dd306940c56.mp4?t=1750976836\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1864720/extras/e6a3411d3a62be0345d507687626523a.poster.avif?t=1750976836\" width=600 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1864720/extras/e6a3411d3a62be0345d507687626523a.webm?t=1750976836\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1864720/extras/e6a3411d3a62be0345d507687626523a.mp4?t=1750976836\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 为电击器积极充电以便击退异化的小镇居民。 </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1864720/extras/afed435d4c8df8c50dc328b4fe4e8e37.poster.avif?t=1750976836\" width=600 height=80 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1864720/extras/afed435d4c8df8c50dc328b4fe4e8e37.webm?t=1750976836\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1864720/extras/afed435d4c8df8c50dc328b4fe4e8e37.mp4?t=1750976836\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1864720/extras/8d71609ef3f59980370129e265876d36.poster.avif?t=1750976836\" width=600 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1864720/extras/8d71609ef3f59980370129e265876d36.webm?t=1750976836\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1864720/extras/8d71609ef3f59980370129e265876d36.mp4?t=1750976836\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 通过屏息来扭曲周遭世界，进而探索新道路，发现新秘密。 </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1864720/extras/db8d55e98af80e33d2851ae100fb060a.poster.avif?t=1750976836\" width=600 height=80 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1864720/extras/db8d55e98af80e33d2851ae100fb060a.webm?t=1750976836\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1864720/extras/db8d55e98af80e33d2851ae100fb060a.mp4?t=1750976836\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1864720/extras/c53614c47d40a3fab1f276a9f5ee66e7.poster.avif?t=1750976836\" width=600 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1864720/extras/c53614c47d40a3fab1f276a9f5ee66e7.webm?t=1750976836\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1864720/extras/c53614c47d40a3fab1f276a9f5ee66e7.mp4?t=1750976836\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1864720/extras/a5c04274858b452975d464b52c7875a4.poster.avif?t=1750976836\" width=600 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1864720/extras/a5c04274858b452975d464b52c7875a4.webm?t=1750976836\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1864720/extras/a5c04274858b452975d464b52c7875a4.mp4?t=1750976836\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 仔细检查周围环境，找到小镇居民遗留的独特物品和笔记。 </p></li></ul>",
